<i>adverb</i>: 의당 [의당], 공정히 [공정히] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>의당 [의당]</dt><br>
<dd>justly; as a matter of course; deservedly</dd><br>
<dd>그렇게 하는 것이 옳으므로 마땅히.</dd><br>
<dd>Naturally because it is right to do so.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>공정히 [공정히]</dt><br>
<dd>fairly; justly</dd><br>
<dd>한쪽으로 치우치지 않고 올바르게.</dd><br>
<dd>Without being one-sided.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>